  "text": "Previous work, including our own, has explored some of the issues relating to defining and evaluating metrics at run-time [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Such metrics can be shown to capture additional information about the program but are, of course, dependent on the context in which the program is run. Indeed it is arguable that metrics at this level represent coverage data, rather than metrics in the usual sense. The use of such information, or its integration into testing strategies, is still relatively undeveloped.",
